snippet: The Jaguars fired Coach Mike Mularkey after just one season. Also, General Manager David Caldwell said the Jets’ Tim Tebow is not in the team’s plans.
abstract: Jacksonville Jaguars fire coach Mike Mularkey after one season, worst in franchise history at 2-14; other NFL developments noted.
lead_paragraph: The Jaguars fired Coach Mike Mularkey after just one season. Also, General Manager David Caldwell said the Jets’ Tim Tebow is not in the team’s plans.

headline.seo: Jaguars Fire Coach Mike Mularkey and Comment on Jets’ Tim Tebow
headline.main: Jaguars Fire First-Year Coach and Deny Interest in the Jets’ Tebow
headline.print_headline: Jaguars Fire First-Year Coach And Deny Interest in the Jets’ Tebow
